TEXT.S: Tungpu daigaz Gaga mniq Nantowseyn Sinyisyang ka alang Tungpu daigaz. 98 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 395 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 92% niqan 362 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 8% niqan 33 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Bunun87%, Truku 1%, Amis 1%, Cou1%, Paiwan 2%, Seejiq/Seediq/Seejiq/Seejiq/Sediq 1%, ni rahuq na o 1%.
